<section xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>2-705</num>
  <heading>Use of official mail by officials-elect.</heading>
  <text>In addition to government employees and elected officials as defined in § <cite path="§2-701">2-701</cite>, the following officials may mail materials as official mail:</text>
  <para>
    <num>(1)</num>
    <text>The Mayor-elect;</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(2)</num>
    <text>The Chairman-elect and members-elect of the Council.</text>
  </para>
